LoopMixer.Loop
public abstract class AbstractEffectable
extends java.lang.Object
implements Effectable

An abstract implementation of Effectable. It keeps track of the effects and will apply only the enabled ones to the signal that passes through process(...).

Author:
Mara Bos (m-ou.se@m-ou.se)
